trans-unit.source: Encapsulates a collection of <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" /> instances and is used for properties whose <see cref="T:System.Type" /> is a collection.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" /> 인스턴스의 컬렉션을 캡슐화하며 <see cref="T:System.Type" />이 컬렉션인 속성에 사용됩니다.

trans-unit.source: The parent <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" />.

Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValueCollection" /> class as a sub-property to the specified parent <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValueCollection" /> 클래스의 새 인스턴스를 지정된 부모 <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" />에 대한 하위 속성으로 초기화합니다.

trans-unit.source: The object to add to the collection.
Adds an object into the collection of <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" /> objects.
The <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" /> for the added object.
Notifies listeners of dynamic changes to the collection, such as when items get added and removed or the whole list is refreshed.
trans-unit.target: 수신자에게 컬렉션에 대한 동적 변경을 알립니다(예: 항목 추가 및 제거 또는 전체 목록 새로 고침).

trans-unit.source: Gets the number of items in a collection of <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" /> 개체의 컬렉션에 있는 항목 수를 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Int32" /> number of items.

Returns a strongly typed <see cref="T:Systems.Collections.IEnumerator" /> that iterates through the collection of <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:Systems.Collections.IEnumerator" /> 개체의 컬렉션을 대상으로 반복하는 강력한 형식의 <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" />를 반환합니다.

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator`1" /> object that can be used to iterate through the collection.
trans-unit.target: 컬렉션을 반복하는 데 사용할 수 있는 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator`1" /> 개체입니다.

trans-unit.source: The object to add to the collection.
The index number that specifies where to insert the object into the collection.
trans-unit.target: 컬렉션에서 개체를 삽입할 위치를 지정하는 인덱스 번호입니다.

trans-unit.source: Inserts a specified object at the specified index in a collection of <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" /> 개체의 컬렉션에서 지정된 인덱스에 지정된 개체를 삽입합니다.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" /> for the added object.
The index of the item to be returned.
Returns a <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" /> from a collection at the given index.
The <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" /> at that index.
Event arguments that contain information about the change in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 컬렉션의 변경 내용에 대한 정보가 포함된 이벤트 인수입니다.

trans-unit.source: Raises the <see cref="E:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValueCollection.CollectionChanged" /> event when items in the collection are added, removed, or resorted.
trans-unit.target: 컬렉션에서 항목이 추가, 제거 또는 다시 정렬되면 <see cref="E:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValueCollection.CollectionChanged" /> 이벤트를 발생시킵니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets the parent <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" /> object that contains the collection.
The <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" /> of the parent.
The item to remove from the collection.
Removes the object from the collection of <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" /> objects.
<see langword="true" /> if removal is successful; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 제거가 성공하면 <see langword="true" />이고, 그렇지 않으면 <see langword="false" />입니다.

trans-unit.source: The host needs to ensure that the PropertyValue is invalid after the object is removed.
trans-unit.target: 호스트는 개체가 제거된 후에 PropertyValue가 유효하지 않은지 확인해야 합니다.

trans-unit.source: The index of the item to remove.
Removes the object from the collection of <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" /> objects at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: 지정된 인덱스에서 <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" /> 개체의 컬렉션에 있는 개체를 제거합니다.

trans-unit.source: The current position index of the object in the collection.
The index position to which the item is moved.
Recalculates the indexes in a collection of <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" /> objects after an existing item is moved to a new position in the collection.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" /> 개체의 컬렉션에서 기존 항목을 컬렉션의 새 위치로 옮긴 후 인덱스를 다시 계산합니다.

trans-unit.source: Returns a strongly typed <see cref="T:Systems.Collections.IEnumerator" /> for a collection of <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:Systems.Collections.IEnumerator" /> 개체의 컬렉션에 대한 강력한 형식의 <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" />를 반환합니다.

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Collections.IEnumerator" /> object that can be used to iterate through the collection.
trans-unit.target: 컬렉션을 반복하는 데 사용할 수 있는 <see cref="T:System.Collections.IEnumerator" /> 개체입니다.
